Pre-Game Insights: Moldova has the chance to promote directly to League C if it wins the group, and in case of a second place, it will play a playoff against one of the last placed teams from League C.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Moldova will play against Malta and Andorra in Group D2 of the UEFA Nations League 2024/25.
Others: The schedule of Moldova's matches in Group D2 of the UEFA Nations League 2024/25 is as follows: September 7, 2024, Moldova - Malta, October 10, 2024, Moldova - Andorra, October 13, 2024, Malta - Moldova, and November 16, 2024, Andorra - Moldova.
